text:
Hi there, I'm trying to make a custom *email template* that uses a deal property to filter a crm_objects query like so:

```{% set country = deal.country %}
{% set query_string = "limit=3&amp;country__eq=" ~ country %}
{% set objects = crm_objects("product", query_string, "name,country") %}
{% for product in objects.results %}
&lt;p&gt;{{ product.name }} - {{ product.country }}&lt;/p&gt;
{% endfor %}```
But I can't make it work, when testing it via email preview and selecting *Deals* -&gt; *My Deal* -&gt; *My Contact* the products are not shown, it feels like if there were different rendering cycles and when the deal is selected the crm_objects has already run and it's always empty.

The idea is to then have a deal-based workflow that will suggest products based on the deal country.
